headline: AffiniPay Named to CNBC’s 2025 List of the World’s Top Fintech Companies
summary: AUSTIN, Texas, July 16, 2025--AffiniPay, a leader in legal practice management software, integrated payments, and embedded fintech solutions for professionals, has been named to CNBC’s list of the World’s Top Fintech Companies of 2025. The company appears in the payments category alongside global leaders including Visa, Adyen, and Affirm.

headline: Mastercard Launches New Benefits, Ultra-Exclusive Card For High Spenders
summary: Mastercard (NYSE:MA) on Wednesday announced it is launching a new set of benefits called The Mastercard Collection to meet a major shift in how people, especially Americans, want to spend their time and money.
